\lang1033\ldblquote Don\rquote t ask questions,\rdblquote  Aunt Petunia snapped.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Are you in touch with wizards?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I told you to get to bed!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What did it mean? Remember the last what?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Go to bed!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote How come \emdash  ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote YOU HEARD YOUR AUNT, NOW GET TO BED!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
