\lang1033\ldblquote No, Harry, the meeting\rquote s only for members of the Order. Ron and Hermione are upstairs, you can wait with them until the meeting\rquote s over and then we\rquote ll have dinner. And keep your voice down in the hall,\rdblquote  she added in an urgent whisper.\lang3081\par
