\lang1033 He led the way out of the door and onto the landing, but before they could descend the stairs \emdash  \ldblquote Hold it!\rdblquote  Ron breathed, flinging out an arm to stop Harry and Hermione walking any farther. \ldblquote They\rquote re still in the hall, we might be able to hear something \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
