\lang1033 Mrs. Weasley had seen him looking. She snatched the plan off the table and stuffed it into Bill\rquote s heavily laden arms.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote This sort of thing ought to be cleared away promptly at the end of meetings,\rdblquote  she snapped before sweeping off toward an ancient dresser from which she started unloading dinner plates.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Bill took out his wand, muttered \ldblquote\i Evanesco\i0 !\rdblquote\i  \i0 and the scrolls vanished.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Sit down, Harry,\rdblquote  said Sirius. \ldblquote You\rquote ve met Mundungus, haven\rquote t you?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
