\lang1033\ldblquote And if you want dinner before midnight I\rquote ll need a hand,\rdblquote  Mrs. Weasley said to the room at large. \ldblquote No, you can stay where you are, Harry dear, you\rquote ve had a long journey \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
