\lang1033\ldblquote\'85 naught to seventy in ten seconds, not bad, is it? When you think the Comet Two Ninety\rquote s only naught to sixty and that\rquote s with a decent tailwind according to \i Which Broomstick\i0 ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
