\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, his best one so far has been six Sickles for a bag of knarl quills,\rdblquote  said George.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Be careful,\rdblquote  Harry warned them quietly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What?\rdblquote  said Fred. \ldblquote Mum\rquote s busy cooing over Prefect Ron, we\rquote re okay.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
