\lang1033\ldblquote WILL YOU LOT GET DOWN HERE NOW, PLEASE!\rdblquote  Mrs. Weasley bellowed and Hermione jumped as though scalded and hurried out of the room. Harry seized Hedwig, stuffed her unceremo\-niously into her cage, and set off downstairs after Hermione, dragging his trunk.\lang3081\par
