\lang1033\ldblquote Nothing,\rdblquote  said Lupin.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote ll still be reporting Sturgis to Dumbledore,\rdblquote  said Moody. \ldblquote That\rquote s the second time he\rquote s not turned up in a week. Getting as unreliable as Mundungus.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, look after yourselves,\rdblquote  said Lupin, shaking hands all round. He reached Harry last and gave him a clap on the shoulder. \ldblquote You too, Harry. Be careful.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, keep your head down and your eyes peeled,\rdblquote  said Moody, shaking Harry\rquote s hand too. \ldblquote And don\rquote t forget, all of you \emdash  careful what you put in writing. If in doubt, don\rquote t put it in a letter at all.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
