\lang1033 The train was gathering still more speed, so that the houses outside the window flashed past and they swayed where they stood.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Shall we go and find a compartment, then?\rdblquote  Harry asked Ron and Hermione.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Ron and Hermione exchanged looks.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Er,\rdblquote  said Ron.\lang3081\par
