\lang1033\ldblquote\i Gone\i0 ?\rdblquote  said Filch, his face contorting with rage.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Gone,\rdblquote  said Harry calmly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Filch opened his mouth furiously, mouthed for a few seconds, then raked Harry\rquote s robes with his eyes. \ldblquote How do I know you haven\rquote t got it in your pocket?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
