\lang1033\ldblquote Wait a moment,\rdblquote  said Hermione suddenly. \ldblquote Oh no \'85 Sirius!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What\rquote s happened?\rdblquote  said Harry, and he snatched at the paper so violently that it ripped down the middle so that he and Hermione were holding half each.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote  \lquote\i The Ministry of Magic has received a tip-off from a reliable source that Sirius Black, notorious mass murderer\lang3081\i0  \lang1033\'85 \i blah blah blah\i0  \'85 \i is cur\-rently hiding in London\i0 !\rquote  \rdblquote\lang3081  \lang1033 Hermione read from her half in an anguished whisper.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Lucius Malfoy, I\rquote ll bet anything,\rdblquote  said Harry in a low, furious voice. \ldblquote He \i did\i0  recognize Sirius on the platform. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
