\lang1033 Ron laughed but Hermione looked upset.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Sirius!\rdblquote  she said reproachfully. \ldblquote Honestly, if you made a bit of an ef\-fort with Kreacher I\rquote m sure he\rquote d respond, after all, you are the only member of his family he\rquote s got left, and Professor Dumbledore said \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote So what are Umbridge\rquote s lessons like?\rdblquote  Sirius interrupted. \ldblquote Is she training you all to kill half-breeds?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote No,\rdblquote  said Harry, ignoring Hermione\rquote s affronted look at being cut off in her defense of Kreacher. \ldblquote She\rquote s not letting us use magic at all!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote All we do is read the stupid textbook,\rdblquote  said Ron.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Ah, well, that figures,\rdblquote  said Sirius. \ldblquote Our information from inside the Ministry is that Fudge doesn\rquote t want you trained in combat.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Trained in combat\i0 ?\rdblquote\i  \i0 repeated Harry incredulously. \ldblquote What does he think we\rquote re doing here, forming some sort of wizard army?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That\rquote s exactly what he thinks you\rquote re doing,\rdblquote  said Sirius, \ldblquote or rather, that\rquote s exactly what he\rquote s afraid Dumbledore\rquote s doing \emdash  forming his own private army, with which he will be able to take on the Ministry of Magic.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 There was a pause at this, then Ron said, \ldblquote That\rquote s the stupidest thing I\rquote ve ever heard, including all the stuff that Luna Lovegood comes out with.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
