\lang1033\ldblquote Yep,\rdblquote  said Sirius. \ldblquote Fudge thinks Dumbledore will stop at nothing to seize power. He\rquote s getting more paranoid about Dumbledore by the day. It\rquote s a matter of time before he has Dumbledore arrested on some trumped-up charge.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
