\lang1033\ldblquote D\rquote you know if there\rquote s going to be anything about Dumbledore in\lang3081  \lang1033 the \i Daily Prophet \i0 tomorrow? Only Ron\rquote s brother Percy reckons there will be \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I don\rquote t know,\rdblquote  said Sirius, \ldblquote I haven\rquote t seen anyone from the Order all weekend, they\rquote re all busy. It\rquote s just been Kreacher and me here. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
