\lang1033\ldblquote Listen, don\rquote t go asking too many questions about Hagrid,\rdblquote  said Sirius hastily, \ldblquote it\rquote ll just draw even more attention to the fact that he\rquote s not back, and I know Dumbledore doesn\rquote t want that. Hagrid\rquote s tough, he\rquote ll be okay.\rdblquote  And when they did not appear cheered by this, Sirius added, \ldblquote When\rquote s your next Hogsmeade weekend anyway? I was think\-ing, we got away with the dog disguise at the station, didn\rquote t we? I thought I could \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
