\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, but we think this time they have,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote Something Malfoy said on the train made us think he knew it was you, and his fa\-ther was on the platform, Sirius \emdash  you know, Lucius Malfoy \emdash  so\lang3081  \lang1033 don\rquote t come up here, whatever you do, if Malfoy recognizes you again \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
