\lang1033\ldblquote Look\lang3081  \lang1033\emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, I\rquote d better get going, I can hear Kreacher coming down the stairs,\rdblquote  said Sirius, but Harry was sure he was lying. \ldblquote I\rquote ll write to tell you a time I can make it back into the fire, then, shall I? If you can stand to risk it?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
