\lang1033 Professor Umbridge\rquote s toadlike smile widened.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Of course,\rdblquote  she said sweetly, making yet another note. \ldblquote Well, if you could just predict something for me, then?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
