\lang1033 Professor Umbridge blinked but recovered her poise almost instantly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, then, you should be able to tell me what Slinkhard says about counterjinxes in chapter fifteen.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote He says that counterjinxes are improperly named,\rdblquote  said Hermione promptly. \ldblquote He says \lquote counterjinx\rquote  is just a name people give their jinxes when they want to make them sound more acceptable.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Professor Umbridge raised her eyebrows, and Harry knew she was impressed against her will.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote But I disagree,\rdblquote  Hermione continued.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Professor Umbridge\rquote s eyebrows rose a little higher and her gaze be\-came distinctly colder.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You disagree?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
