\lang1033\ldblquote But \emdash\rdblquote  Hermione began.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That is enough,\rdblquote  said Professor Umbridge. She walked back to the front of the class and stood before them, all the jauntiness she had shown at the beginning of the lesson gone. \ldblquote Miss Granger, I am going to take five points from Gryffindor House.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 There was an outbreak of muttering at this.\lang3081\par
