\lang1033 Harry did not speak to Hermione all through Charms, but when they entered Transfiguration he forgot his anger; Professor Umbridge and her clipboard were sitting in a corner and the sight of her drove the memory of breakfast right out of his head.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Excellent,\rdblquote  whispered Ron, as they sat down in their usual seats. \ldblquote Let\rquote s see Umbridge get what she deserves.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Professor McGonagall marched into the room without giving the slightest indication that she knew Professor Umbridge was there.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That will do,\rdblquote  she said and silence fell immediately. \ldblquote Mr. Finni\-gan, kindly come here and hand back the homework \emdash  Miss Brown, please take this box of mice \emdash  don\rquote t be silly, girl, they won\rquote t hurt you \emdash  and hand one to each student \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Hem, hem,\i0\rdblquote  said Professor Umbridge, employing the same silly little cough she had used to interrupt Dumbledore on the first night of term. Professor McGonagall ignored her. Seamus handed back Harry\rquote s essay; Harry took it without looking at him and saw, to his relief, that he had managed an A.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Right then, everyone, listen closely \emdash  Dean Thomas, if you do that to the mouse again I shall put you in detention \emdash  most of you have now successfully vanished your snails and even those who were left with a certain amount of shell have the gist of the spell. Today we shall be \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Hem, hem,\i0\rdblquote\lang3081  \lang1033 said Professor Umbridge.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Yes\i0 ?\rdblquote  said Professor McGonagall, turning round, her eyebrows so close together they seemed to form one long, severe line.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I was just wondering, Professor, whether you received my note telling you of the date and time of your inspec \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
