\lang1033\ldblquote Me,\rdblquote  said Ron, who was still rather disheveled. \ldblquote I didn\rquote t realize that would happen. It\rquote s not fair!\rdblquote  he added to Harry, as the girls headed off for the portrait hole, still giggling madly. \ldblquote Hermione\rquote s al\-lowed in our dormitory, how come we\rquote re not allowed \emdash  ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
