\lang1033\ldblquote They can\rquote t have done,\rdblquote  said Hermione in a low voice.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You\rquote re so naive,\rdblquote  said Ron, \ldblquote you think just because you\rquote re all hon\-orable and trustworthy \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
