\lang1033\ldblquote What\rquote ll happen to them?\rdblquote  said Ron eagerly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, put it this way,\rdblquote  said Hermione, \ldblquote it\rquote ll make Eloise Midgen\rquote s acne look like a couple of cute freckles. Come on, let\rquote s get down to breakfast and see what the others think. \'85 I wonder whether this has been put up in all the Houses?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 It was immediately apparent on entering the Great Hall that Um\-bridge\rquote s sign had not only appeared in Gryffindor Tower. There was a peculiar intensity about the chatter and an extra measure of move\-ment in the Hall as people scurried up and down their tables confer\-ring on what they had read. Harry, Ron, and Hermione had barely taken their seats when Neville, Dean, Fred, George, and Ginny de\-scended upon them.\lang3081\par
