\lang1033\ldblquote We\rquote re going to do it anyway, of course,\rdblquote  he said quietly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Knew you\rquote d say that,\rdblquote  said George, beaming and thumping Harry on the arm.\lang3081\par
