\lang1033\ldblquote Never mind spots, the idiots can\rquote t come over here now, it\rquote ll look\lang3081  \lang1033 really suspicious \emdash  sit down!\rdblquote  she mouthed to Ernie and Hannah, gesturing frantically to them to rejoin the Hufflepuff table. \ldblquote Later! We\rquote ll \emdash  talk \emdash  to \emdash  you \emdash  \i later\i0 !\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote ll tell Michael,\rdblquote  said Ginny impatiently, swinging herself off her bench. \ldblquote The fool, honestly \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 She hurried off toward the Ravenclaw table; Harry watched her go. Cho was sitting not far away, talking to the curly-haired friend she had brought along to the Hog\rquote s Head. Would Umbridge\rquote s notice scare her off meeting them again?\lang3081\par
