\lang1033\ldblquote No, Professor!\rdblquote  said Harry hastily.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well then, why are you out of class?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote It\rquote s \i urgent,\i0  apparently,\rdblquote  said the second gargoyle snidely.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m looking for Professor Grubbly-Plank,\rdblquote  Harry explained. \ldblquote It\rquote s my owl, she\rquote s injured.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
