\lang1033 Harry neither knew nor cared what thestrals were, he just wanted to know that Hedwig was going to be all right. Professor McGonagall, however, looked sharply at Harry and said, \ldblquote Do you know how far this owl\rquote s traveled, Potter?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
