\lang1033\ldblquote Oh yeah!\rdblquote  said Harry, who had momentarily forgotten the scroll tied to Hedwig\rquote s leg. Professor Grubbly-Plank handed it over and then disappeared into the staffroom carrying Hedwig, who was staring at Harry as though unable to believe he would give her away like this. Feeling slightly guilty, he turned to go, but Professor McGonagall called him back.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Potter!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes, Professor?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
