\lang1033\ldblquote I \emdash\rdblquote  said Harry, but the flood of students rolling along the corri\-dor was almost upon him. Professor McGonagall gave him a curt nod and retreated into the staffroom, leaving Harry to be swept out into the courtyard with the crowd. Here he spotted Ron and Hermione al\-ready standing in a sheltered corner, their cloak collars turned up against the wind. Harry slit open the scroll as he hurried toward them and found five words in Sirius\rquote s handwriting:\par
