\lang1033 They trudged down the stone steps to the dungeons for Potions, all three of them lost in thought, but as they reached the bottom of the stairs they were recalled to themselves by the voice of Draco Malfoy, who was standing just outside Snape\rquote s classroom door, waving around an official-looking piece of parchment and talking much louder than was necessary so that they could hear every word.\lang3081\par
