\lang1033 It became clear after ten minutes, however, that Ron was not capa\-ble of eating anything more and Harry thought it best to get him\lang3081  \lang1033 down to the changing rooms. As they rose from the table, Hermione got up too, and taking Harry\rquote s arm, she drew him to one side.\lang3081\par
