\lang1033\ldblquote Well, I don\rquote t know,\rdblquote  Hermione admitted. \ldblquote That \i is\i0  a bit odd. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote So what\rquote s in the Department of Mysteries?\rdblquote  Harry asked Ron. \ldblquote Has your dad ever mentioned anything about it?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
