\lang1033\ldblquote It\rquote s not weird at all, it makes perfect sense,\rdblquote  said Hermione. \ldblquote It will be something top secret that the Ministry has been developing, I ex\-pect. \'85 Harry, are you sure you\rquote re all right?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
