\lang1033\ldblquote How do those hats work, then?\rdblquote  said Hermione, distracted from her homework and watching Fred and George. \ldblquote I mean, obviously it\rquote s some kind of Invisibility Spell, but it\rquote s rather clever to have extended the field of invisibility beyond the boundaries of the charmed object. \'85 I\rquote d imagine the charm wouldn\rquote t have a very long life though. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
