\lang1033 He opened his eyes and as he did so, he became aware that the wild laughter was coming out of his own mouth. The moment he realized this, it died away; Harry lay panting on the floor, staring up at the ceiling, the scar on his forehead throbbing horribly. Ron was bending over him, looking very worried.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What happened?\rdblquote  he said.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\lang3081  \lang1033\'85 dunno \'85\rdblquote  Harry gasped, sitting up again. \ldblquote He\rquote s really happy \'85 really happy \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
