\lang1033 The dormitory door opened; Dean and Seamus came in. Harry swung his legs back into bed. He did not want to look as though any\-thing odd had just happened, seeing as Seamus had only just stopped thinking Harry was a nutter.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Did you say,\rdblquote  murmured Ron, putting his head close to Harry\rquote s on the pretense of helping himself to water from the jug on his bedside table, \ldblquote that you \i were\i0  You-Know-Who?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah,\rdblquote  said Harry quietly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Ron took an unnecessarily large gulp of water. Harry saw it spill over his chin onto his chest.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Harry,\rdblquote  he said, as Dean and Seamus clattered around noisily, pulling off their robes, and talking, \ldblquote you\rquote ve got to tell \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
