\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote ve got the form, Headmistress,\rdblquote  he said hoarsely, waving the piece of parchment Harry had just seen him take from her desk. \ldblquote I\rquote ve got the form and I\rquote ve got the whips waiting. \'85 Oh, let me do it now. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Very good, Argus,\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote You two,\rdblquote  she went on, gazing down at Fred and George, \ldblquote are about to learn what happens to wrongdoers in my school.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
