\lang1033\ldblquote I mean, I can\rquote t get any worse, can I?\rdblquote  he told Harry and Hermione grimly over breakfast on the morning of the match. \ldblquote Nothing to lose now, is there?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You know,\rdblquote  said Hermione, as she and Harry walked down to the pitch a little later in the midst of a very excitable crowd, \ldblquote I think Ron might do better without Fred and George around. They never exactly gave him a lot of confidence. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
