\lang1033 They found seats in the topmost row of the stands. It was a fine, clear day. Ron could not wish for better, and Harry found himself hoping against hope that Ron would not give the Slytherins cause for more rousing choruses of \ldblquote Weasley Is Our King.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
