\lang1033\ldblquote I wish to interrogate him!\rdblquote  shouted Umbridge angrily, and Snape looked away from Harry back into her furiously quivering face. \ldblquote I wish you to provide me with a potion that will force him to tell me the truth!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
