\lang1033 Snape looked back at Harry, who stared at him, frantic to commu\-nicate without words.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\i Voldemort\rquote s got Sirius in the Department of Mysteries,\i0  he thought des\-perately. \i Voldemort\rquote s got Sirius \i0\emdash\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You are on probation!\rdblquote  shrieked Professor Umbridge, and Snape looked back at her, his eyebrows slightly raised. \ldblquote You are being delib\-erately unhelpful! I expected better, Lucius Malfoy always speaks most highly of you! Now get out of my office!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
