\lang1033\ldblquote I am a fully qualified Ministry official, Malfoy, do you really think\lang3081  \lang1033 I cannot manage two wandless teenagers alone?\rdblquote  asked Umbridge sharply. \ldblquote In any case, it does not sound as though this weapon is something that schoolchildren should see. You will remain here until I return and make sure none of these\rdblquote  \emdash  she gestured around at Ron, Ginny, Neville, and Luna \emdash  \ldblquote escape.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote All right,\rdblquote  said Malfoy, looking sulky and disappointed.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote And you two can go ahead of me and show me the way,\rdblquote  said Um\-bridge, pointing at Harry and Hermione with her wand. \ldblquote Lead on. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\par
