\lang1033\ldblquote We urge the magical population to remain vigi\-lant. The Ministry is currently publishing guides to elementary home and personal defense that will be\lang3081  \lang1033 delivered free to all Wizarding homes within the coming month.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 The Minister\rquote s statement was met with dismay and alarm from the Wizarding community, which as re\-cently as last Wednesday was receiving Ministry as\-surances that there was \ldblquote no truth whatsoever in these persistent rumors that You-Know-Who is operating amongst us once more.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
