\lang1033\ldblquote He\rquote s \lquote the Boy Who Lived\rquote  again now, though, isn\rquote t he?\rdblquote  said Ron darkly. \ldblquote Not such a show-off maniac anymore, eh?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
