\lang1033\ldblquote Ah. I see there are no longer any points left in the Gryffindor hour\-glass to take away. In that case, Potter, we will simply have to \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Add some more?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Professor McGonagall had just stumped up the stone steps into the castle. She was carrying a tartan carpetbag in one hand and leaning heavily on a walking stick with her other, but otherwise looked quite well.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Professor McGonagall!\rdblquote  said Snape, striding forward. \ldblquote Out of St. Mungo\rquote s, I see!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes, Professor Snape,\rdblquote  said Professor McGonagall, shrugging off her traveling cloak, \ldblquote I\rquote m quite as good as new. You two \emdash  Crabbe \emdash  Goyle \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
