\lang1033 Hagrid broke off, cleared his throat gruffly, looked at Harry, and took a long draft of juice.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Anyway, back now,\rdblquote  he said feebly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You \emdash  you look better,\rdblquote  said Harry, who was determined to keep the conversation moving away from Sirius.\lang3081\par
